                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  [1m[38;5;252m## User-visible / Behavior Changes[0m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  • [38;5;189m`senseaudio`[39m appears in [38;5;189m`openclaw infer tts providers`[39m, "configured" when
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  [38;5;189m`SENSEAUDIO_API_KEY`[39m is in env or [38;5;189m`messages.tts.providers.senseaudio.apiKey`[39m.
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  • [38;5;189m`openclaw infer tts voices --provider senseaudio`[39m lists the upstream system
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  voices.
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  • [38;5;189m`openclaw infer tts convert --model senseaudio/senseaudio-tts-1.5-260319 ...`[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  returns MP3 (or opus for voice-note channel targets).
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  • [38;5;189m`autoSelectOrder: 45`[39m — strictly behind ElevenLabs (20), Azure (30), MiniMax
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  (40).
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  Existing user defaults are not displaced.
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  • Defaults: voice [38;5;189m`female_0033_b`[39m, model [38;5;189m`senseaudio-tts-1.5-260319`[39m, base URL
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  [38;5;189m`https://api.senseaudio.cn`[39m, MP3 32 kHz / 128 kbps / stereo.
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  • No new env vars / config keys / CLI flags. [38;5;189m`SENSEAUDIO_API_KEY`[39m was already
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  declared by the ASR side.
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  [1m[38;5;252m## Diagram (if applicable)[0m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  [38;5;251maudio-file target:[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  [38;5;251m  tts.convert -> senseaudio.synthesize[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m                [38;5;251m-> POST /v1/t2a_v2 -> hex audio[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m                [38;5;251m-> Buffer.from(hex) -> MP3 (voiceCompatible=false)[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  [38;5;251mvoice-note target:[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  [38;5;251m  tts.convert (channel=voice-note) -> senseaudio.synthesize[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m                [38;5;251m-> POST /v1/t2a_v2 -> MP3[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m                [38;5;251m-> transcodeAudioBufferToOpus (ffmpeg)[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m                [38;5;251m-> opus (voiceCompatible=true) -> messenger voice-note bubble[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  [38;5;251mvoice picker:[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  [38;5;251m  talk UI -> senseaudio.listVoices[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  [38;5;251m          -> POST /v1/get_voice {voice_type: "system"}[39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m  [38;5;251m          -> map system_voice[] -> SpeechVoiceOption[][39m
                                                                        [38;5;244m│[39m
